#

Seared Scallops with Garlic Lemon Butter

20 min
$25
400 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

shellfish

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freelow-carbhigh-protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

main course

Tags:

seafoodquickgourmet

Description

Perfectly seared scallops drizzled with a rich garlic lemon butter sauce, ready in just 20 minutes!

Ingredients

  • scallops: 1 pound
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • garlic: 3 cloves
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: for garnish
